1432	/// rbw-dU empty-arg refusal — BBAA9 contract. Invoking rbw-dU with no
1433	/// argument must die non-zero and emit the rbw-dl pointer (operator
1434	/// discovery for candidate depot project IDs). BUW dispatch merges
1435	/// stderr→stdout via `2>&1` (bud_dispatch.sh:372), so the captured
1436	/// stdout carries the buc_warn/buc_info/buc_tabtarget/buc_die output
1437	/// from rbgp_depot_unmake's no-arg branch (rbgp_Payor.sh:937-942).
